title: Kittikhun khō̜ng Phra Yēsū Khrit rīaprīang dōi Thān Yōhan.
Padan si Mbaroe, e me kap berita si mehoeli kerna Toehanta Jesoes Kristoes / si noesoerkentja ibas tjakap Batak-Karo, J. H. Neumann.
Kniga proroka Daniila na osetinskom i︠a︡zyke.
Kitāb-e muqaddas, yaʻnī kutub-e ʻAhd-e ʻanīq u ʻAhd-e jadīd, ke az zabānhā-ye aslī-ye ʻIbrānī u Ārāmī u Yūnānī tarjama shode ast.
